        <updateDate>2021-02-02T19:44:49Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No Budget, No Pay Act </b></p> <p>This bill withholds the salaries of Members of a chamber of Congress that has not agreed to a budget resolution for FY2022 by April 15, 2021, as required by the Congressional Budget Act of 1974. </p> <p>Salaries are withheld from April 16, 2021, until the earlier of (1) the day on which the chamber of Congress agrees to a budget resolution, or (2) the last day of the 117th Congress.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
