      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide that the salaries of Members of a House of Congress will be held in escrow if that House has not agreed to a concurrent resolution on the budget for fiscal year 2022 by April 15, 2021.</title>
      </item>
